{
  "stem": "27509.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, obviously, as long as you are at school, your friends are your school friends.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or if you are going to a youth movement, you make some friends there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I've had some connection with the Mizrahi youth movement, called in those days [HEBREW], the equivalent of what we've got here B'nai Akiva.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But essentially, it-- through the duration of-- of-- of secondary school, it was my school friends that was my world.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was my world.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Exclusively Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There wasn't-- it was a Hebrew gymnasium, where every-- every subject-- excuse me-- was taught in Hebrew, with the exception of Polish literature, Polish history, and Polish geography that were taught in Polish.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything else, including my Latin, was translated into Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my algebra and my-- everything was in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So of course, and not only that, but we were, by and large, of the same [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the social structure of the community, of the people who came there were, with some exceptions-- and the exception that proved the rule-- were of the same social-- socioeconomic strata.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I had one exception in particular that now that you've asked the question, I never thought about it before.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That brings me to mind-- brings that particular instance to mind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And maybe it has to be recorded because even though Bialystok was, in economic terms, a-- an outstanding example of self-governing and self-supporting community economically, there was plenty of poverty, obviously, even there and then, as it is in any community.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this one person with whom I shared a bench in the school is-- is standing out as the antithesis of that-- of that milieu.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was thin, drawn, and his right arm was paralyzed, but to be paralyzed from birth or paralyzed later, I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
